                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9808" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0259</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">844 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“链”通数字“澜”途：海澜之家供应链数字化转型记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bridging the Chain to Digital Waves: The Digital Transformation Journey of HLA&#39;s Supply Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李秀珠，陈丽敏，苏毓璇，吕晓菲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海澜之家集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海澜之家；供应链；数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HLA;Supply Chain;Digital Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字化浪潮重塑全球产业格局的时代，传统服装企业曾依靠稳定供应链与广泛销售渠道占据市场，随着新消费时代到来，消费者需求多样化、个性化与市场竞争加剧，传统模式暴露出库存积压、供应链响应滞后等问题。本案例以海澜之家供应链数字化转型为主线，描述了面对消费需求碎片化、市场竞争加剧等挑战，海澜之家以“数据驱动”为核心，通过分阶段推进战略布局，逐步搭建起高效、灵活且智能化的供应链体系，完成了从传统制造模式向科技赋能模式的转型跨越。本案例旨在引导学员深入学习供应链进行数字化转型背后的驱动因素，了解实现数字化转型成功的核心要素及其未来演进趋势，掌握通过数字技术持续强化供应链弹性的方法，同时期望对新时期供应链数字化赋能传统服装行业转型升级具有借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the era of digital wave reshaping the global industrial structure, traditional clothing enterprises used to rely on stable supply chains and extensive sales channels to occupy the market, with the arrival of the new consumption era, consumer demand diversification, personalized and market competition intensified, the traditional model exposed inventory backlog, supply chain response lag and other problems. This case takes the digital transformation of Heilan Home&#39;s supply chain as the main line, and describes that in the face of challenges such as fragmented consumer demand and intensifying market competition, Heilan Home takes &quot;data-driven&quot; as the core, and gradually builds an efficient, flexible and intelligent supply chain system by promoting the strategic layout in stages, completing the transformation from the traditional manufacturing mode to the technology enabling mode. This case aims to guide students to learn the driving factors behind the digital transformation of the supply chain, understand the core elements of the success of digital transformation and its future evolution trend, master the method of continuously strengthening the elasticity of the supply chain through digital technology, and hope to provide reference for the transformation and upgrading of the traditional clothing industry in the new era.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《数字化供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链数字化转型的定义和动因；数字化供应链转型升级模式的演进形态；供应链协同理论；供应链韧性；价值链理论；动态能力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
